{"tid":1172418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 福建劇院舞台坍塌　1死14傷包括兒童","createTime":"2019-05-26T12:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T13:04:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c66209d248a64eca418c6c70b29b453b58b87db","tid":1172418,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"福建漳州金水仙大劇院周六（25日）夜晚發生致命事故，一群兒童和教師在舞蹈比賽後於舞台上合照，其間舞台中央的升降台突然坍塌，站在升降台上的多名師生跌入坑內，造成一名13歲兒童死亡，另有14人受傷。現時警方已經拘留主辦單位相關人等。<br />\n內地傳媒翻查資料，發現涉事比賽是由昆明雀神文化傳播公司主辦，該公司在網絡稱，是內地著名舞蹈藝術家楊麗萍發起成立的「全國性連鎖文化藝術交流與藝術人才培養教育機構」<br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190526/s00004/1558855368945/福建劇院舞台坍塌-1死14傷包括兒童【短片】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190526%2Fs00004%2F1558855368945%2F%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E5%8A%87%E9%99%A2%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E5%9D%8D%E5%A1%8C-1%E6%AD%BB14%E5%82%B7%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BdiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=928003f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190526%2Fs00004%2F1558855368945%2F%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E5%8A%87%E9%99%A2%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E5%9D%8D%E5%A1%8C-1%E6%AD%BB14%E5%82%B7%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91&h=d9ad16bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190526/s00004/1558855368945/福建劇院舞台坍塌-1死14傷包括兒童【短片】</a>"},{"pid":"0f6aa01f680b1653ef128723520fc9d23b82f7bb","tid":1172418,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda184404bfaa7d57742e81302c3a71952b91574","tid":1172418,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"你還有黨呀"},{"pid":"656f33f8ad8918c86659ec3805ad050a023